{"tid":1534572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鑑古知今系列] 孟子教大家點解殺人係啱","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:07:41.000Z","uid":127543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27f3a29b1ebaaac0b11e766912c936a57fce82e4","tid":1534572,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"〈新註孟子白話解說．卷十四．盡心下〉<br />\n齊宣王問曰：「湯放桀，武王伐紂，有諸？」<br />\n孟子對曰：「於傳有之。」<br />\n曰：「臣弒其君可乎？」<br />\n曰：「賊仁者謂之賊，賊義者謂之殘，殘賊之人謂之一夫。<span style=\"color: red;\">聞誅一夫紂矣，未聞弒君也。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n易入口版本：<br />\n孟子比人問，周武王殺咗商紂喎，咁咪係弒君囉？<br />\n孟子就答，\b商紂殘害百姓喎，已經唔係君主而係一個普通男人。周武王誅殺咗個男人，唔係弒君喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古時誅殺暴政既俠義之風隨住歷史流逝都消亡得七七八八。<br />\n原來殺人係咁有力量，多謝孟子的教導。"},{"pid":"b1f78f7ccb7966f472b7a3c6e833a92d8232c200","tid":1534572,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"679c0b93e96d181991f24deb35015c4e4afc608c","tid":1534572,"uid":52477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"儒家乃華夏之本，可行。擺出華夏正宗姿態，毛澤東都無你符。"},{"pid":"a7ba86118023ffbbc9fa097f24e3a6321c7b4e62","tid":1534572,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"76009da42dde92833fc09d2a522828d03e63675b","tid":1534572,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"bb35bc534aea09f7b3642bf91d4a766ef1934ec5","tid":1534572,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"一於9月28孔聖誕去黃大仙祠拜孔子<br />\n宗教集會唔洗申請"},{"pid":"086043e3efb7dd6a82232b9b47d0a8bda1122b8e","tid":1534572,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f3a29b1ebaaac0b11e766912c936a57fce82e4","tid":1534572,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"〈新註孟子白話解說．卷十四．盡心下〉<br />\n齊宣王問曰：「湯放桀，武王伐紂，有諸？」<br />\n孟子對曰：「於傳有之。」<br />\n曰：「臣弒其君可乎？」<br />\n曰：「賊仁者謂之賊，賊義者謂之殘，殘賊之人謂之一夫。<span style=\"color: red;\">聞誅一夫紂矣，未聞弒君也。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n易入口版本：<br />\n孟子比人問，周武王殺咗商紂喎，咁咪係弒君囉？<br />\n孟子就答，\b商紂殘害百姓喎，已經唔係君主而係一個普通男人。周武王誅殺咗個男人，唔係弒君喎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n古時誅殺暴政既俠義之風隨住歷史流逝都消亡得七七八八。<br />\n原來殺人係咁有力量，多謝孟子的教導。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"孟子解釋話 一夫=一條仆街<br />\n孟子意思話武王殺左一條仆街 係替天行道"},{"pid":"821cfbadca89bfc0ae1fd792eaea4288ad882657","tid":1534572,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b803b0a2e7d7e4ba618825fa44c5bb6c6dd97894","tid":1534572,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"其實係要講名要符實，有君之名唔行君之實，所以唔應該叫佢君，而要叫佢一夫，同時可以推佢下台而唔叫弑。"}]}